      "para_id": "Q000972.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Inana , his lady , Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , built ( and ) restored the E-dur-anki . He dedicated this ( door socket ) for his well-being to her ."
    }
